text: Kroken Church is a church in Kroken, Norway which is part of the city of Tromsø. It is part of the Kroken parish, which is part of the Tromsø domprosti. The church was built in 2006 and has a fan-shaped design. It can hold around 600 people. == References == Category:Buildings and structures in Troms Category:Churches in Tromsø
